text: José Ángel Efa Nchama (born 29 January 1992) is an Equatorial Guinean footballer who plays as a forward for Leones Vegetarianos FC and the Equatorial Guinea national team. ==International career== Efa made his international debut for Equatorial Guinea on 28 July 2019. ===International goals=== :Scores and results list Equatorial Guinea's goal tally first. {| class="wikitable" style="font-size:100%;" !
